Love Song

No Description

Old Fashioned Kisses

Nick loves for me to wear mod clothes... and I bought this micro-mini because I knew he'd go ape for me in it! Nick isn't the only one who goes ape, though... dad goes into orbit.

Jonnie Love: One Kiss

Jonnie Love believes that this kiss is a beginning... but Paula didn't come here alone... and the group who call themselves 'Satan's Horde' may see that this kiss is the beginning of the end for Jonnie Love!

Strange Kisses

The first time I kissed him... we were strangers... but I felt as if I belonged there in his arms! This was a beach party at Loon Lake... and the kiss was part of a game we were playing!
name: Strange Kisses

description:
I Was Alone...

No Description

A Kiss For Carol

I knew dad had hopes for me... he and mom had always thought I was intelligent and I hated to bring home the poor marks I began to get when I was a junior in high! I could do better... but I just didn't have the time! Because I wanted Lew Nash to notice me and I'd never catch his eye if I kept my head buried in a book at the library!

So Far From Love

We were in love, Hank and I, we had been since we met a year before at a high school dance/older people may think it was just puppy-love, but we knew it wasn't... it was real love! Why, we even planned for the future! And out marriage which we knew couldn't happen for a few years! But while we planned, I had no idea what that future had in store for me, and how it would change my life!

Love Or Pity? (Text Only Story)

Join the Club

When Billy Clay took me in his arms, there was a difference from the shy, unpracticed kisses of other boys in school! Billy had had other steady girls... but, as I returned his kiss, I vowed to myself that I would be his last!
name: Join The Club
Troubled Kisses; But I'm Different... Now!; Jonnie Love: The Girl In The Fiery Ring

description: The Captain's journey home takes a disastrous turn on the high seas when a rogue naval force targets him for destruction. The long war in the Middle East is complete, but the danger is far from over.
name: Red Sky at Morning

description:
Wild Kisses

This is a bad scene but I get a wild, perverse joy from being in Kinner's arms, taking his kisses.....

What Does Anyone Know?

I know what everyone says about Robbie but I don't care... he's the only boy in the world I can ever love!

Another's Love

When I see Gail kissing Michael, I practically swoon with envy... he's too much, real groovy, and I think if I could be in his arms instead of Gail, I'd never want another boy!

Cry Among Strangers

I love the high school I go to here in the city... it's really wild and Larry and I have a blast every week-end! I never want it to end... but this will be the last date I'll have with Larry for a long, long time!

You see... dad resigned from the company he's with... and we're moving to the Midwest... and I'm heartbroken already!
name: Cry Among Strangers

description:
Hibiki is a student in a magic school. Try as she might, her only real skill seems to be making a pot of delicious tea... Or is it?! This heartwarming fantasy story from the artist behind the .hack manga will have you believing in the power of magic!

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter 1: The Magic of Transposition
  • Chapter 2: The Magic That Cannot Heal [Part 1]
  • Chapter 3: The Magic That Cannot Heal [Part 2]
  • Chapter 4: The Magic of Life [Part 1]
  • Chapter 5: The Magic of Life [Part 2]
  • Chapter 6: The Magic of Life [Part 3]
  • Side Story: "Even If I Forget You"
name: Vol. 1

description:
When we last saw Hibiki, she was helping a lonely single mother try to overcome her heartbreaking sadness. Hibiki's magic, she has discovered, exists to save people, and to help with living but is her magic powerful enough to save herself? Back at the academy, a monster threatens the students, and it's up to Hibiki to rescue her friends--and the monster. Later, the school falls under the spell of a magical harmonica that gives everyone the moody blues. Will Hibiki's power be enough to overcome this cursed rhythm?

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter 7: The Magic That Protects All
  • Chapter 8: The Magic of the Cursed Item
  • Chapter 9: The Magic of the Heart
  • Chapter 10: The Magic of the Demon
  • Chapter 11: The Magic That Saves
  • Bonus Story: Our Beginning Song
name: Vol. 2

description:
From the pages of Kevin Smith's Green Hornet comes this thrilling lead-in story, starring Mulan Kato, daughter of the Green Hornet's faithful companion, Kato! Learn the secrets of Kato, his daughter, his wife's murder and the mysterious Black Hornet, in a series that serves as a prequel to Kevin Smith's Green Hornet.

Collects issues #1-5, along with a complete cover gallery.
name: TPB
